settings.autoradio-craziness-description: Ang Autoradio ay mamimili ng mga kanta na lalong kakaiba sa mga kanta na nasa pila
settings.autoradio-description: Kusang magdagdag ng katulad na kanta pag paubos na ang nasa pila
settings.listening-history-description: Log the tracks you listen to, a la Last.fm. The history is stored offline.
settings.compact-menu-bar: Gamitin ang compact style para sa menu bar
settings.compact-queue-bar: Gamitin ang compact style para sa bar ng mga nakapilang kanta
settings.disable-gpu: Huwag paganahin ang hardware rendering (maaaring maayos ang isyu sa pag-drag ng mga bagay at pag-flash ng screen)
settings.downloads-count: Pinakamataas na limit sa sabayang pagdownload
settings.github-description: Log in gamit ang Github para makagawa at makabahagi ng iyong mga playlist online (upcoming feature).
settings.lastfm-description: Para i-enable ang scrobbling, kailangan mo muna i-connect at i-authorize ang Nuclear sa Last.fm, tapos pindutin ang log in.
settings.loop-after-queue-end: i-loop pagkatapos patugtugin ang huling nasa pila
settings.mastodon-authorized: Ang Nuclear ay awtorisadong magpost sa
settings.mastodon-awaiting-authorization: Ang Nuclear ay naka-register na sa {{instanceUrl}}. Hintayin ang awtorisasyon.
settings.mastodon-post-format-description: Nuclear will post a status on Mastodon after each track completes playing. The above string will be the template for each post, with {{artist}}, {{title}}, and {{url}} replaced with the artist, title, and a link to the track respectively.
settings.normalize-description: Automatically adjust volume of tracks so that they are played at the same level. This needs to fetch the whole track to work, so it may cause a delay between tracks.
settings.seek-iteration: Bilang ng segunda sa pag-seek forward/backward pag nakapindot ang arrow keys
settings.shuffle-when-going-back: I-shuffle pag punta sa nakaraang kanta
settings.shuffle-when-going-back-description: Magplay ng random na kanta pag aktiba ang shuffle at nakapindot ang pindutan ng nakaraang kanta
settings.skip-sponsorblock-description: Playback skips non-music segment from SponsorBlock (https://sponsor.ajay.app/)
settings.track-duration: Ipakita ang track duration sa ibabaw ng seekbar
settings.use-stream-verification-description: Use stream verification. Loads the streams the community has verified as being correct for the tracks you play. Also allows you to vote on streams. See documentation for details.
